StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetMepsVisitedLastForNwa]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @NwaID int ) AS
SELECT TOP 1 o.MEPS_NAME FROM dbo.MEPS_SCHEDULE s WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN dbo.MEPS_ORGANIZATION_LOOKUP o on s.MEPS_ORGANIZATION_ID = o.MEPS_ORGANIZATION_ID WHERE NWA_ID = @NwaID AND PROCESSING_STATUS = 'S'
